trans-unit.source: Represents a user identity authenticated using forms authentication.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en bruker-ID som er godkjent bruker skjemagodkjenning.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The FormsIdentity class is used by the <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationModule> when a user is authenticated with forms authentication.
trans-unit.target: Klassen FormsIdentity brukes av den <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationModule>når en bruker er godkjent med skjemagodkjenning.</xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: An instance of the FormsIdentity class is created using the <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket> that is decrypted from the forms-authentication cookie or from the URL.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av klassen FormsIdentity opprettes ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket>som dekrypteres fra informasjonskapsler for skjemagodkjenning eller URL-adressen.</xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket>

trans-unit.source: The new instance of the FormsIdentity class is used to construct a new <xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal> object that is set as the value of the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property for the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: Den nye forekomsten av klassen FormsIdentity brukes til å lage et nytt <xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal>objekt som er angitt som verdien for <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>egenskapen for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The authentication ticket upon which this identity is based.
trans-unit.target: Godkjenningsbilletten som identiteten er basert.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"></xref> class based on the specified identity.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"> </xref> klassen basert på de angitte identitet.

trans-unit.source: The identity upon which this identity is based.
trans-unit.target: Identiteten som identiteten er basert på.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of authenticated identity.
trans-unit.target: Henter typen godkjente identiteten.

trans-unit.source: The type of authenticated identity.
trans-unit.target: Hva slags godkjente identiteten.

trans-unit.source: This property always returns "Forms".
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer alltid "Skjemaer".

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of claims that are associated with this identity.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av krav som er tilknyttet denne identiteten.

trans-unit.source: The collection of claims.
trans-unit.target: Samling av krav.

trans-unit.source: Gets a copy of the current <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter en kopi av gjeldende <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the current <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: En kopi av gjeldende <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether authentication took place.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om godkjenning, fant sted.

trans-unit.source: This property always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the user name of the forms identity.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på identiteten skjemaer.

trans-unit.source: The Name property returns the value of the <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket.Name%2A> property from the <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket> supplied to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Name returnerer verdien for den <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket.Name%2A>egenskapen fra den <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket>angitt til konstruktøren.</xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket> </xref:System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The user name of the forms identity.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på skjemaer-identitet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket"></xref> for the forms-authentication user identity.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket"> </xref> for skjemagodkjenning brukeridentiteten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket"></xref> supplied to the <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity.%23ctor%2A> constructor for the current object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.Security.FormsAuthenticationTicket"> </xref> angitt for den <xref:System.Web.Security.FormsIdentity.%23ctor%2A> konstruktøren for det gjeldende objektet.
